    "description": "Here's the Simplified Chinese translation with the formatting preserved:<br><br>---<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/0278e4ab4d578239fcd0288a5a05f255.poster.avif?t=1771887294\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/0278e4ab4d578239fcd0288a5a05f255.webm?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/0278e4ab4d578239fcd0288a5a05f255.mp4?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>**Project Castaway** 是一款生存制作游戏，背景设定在广袤的太平洋。狩猎、收集、砍伐树木并展开探险，穿越海洋，发现充满独特资源的荒岛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/a2f8729298e630a4d19864658e2c3c78.webp?t=1771887294\" width=459 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/64c1caf188a4fd4fdb8b2f419f30156c.poster.avif?t=1771887294\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/64c1caf188a4fd4fdb8b2f419f30156c.webm?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/64c1caf188a4fd4fdb8b2f419f30156c.mp4?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>体验一个真正的流浪者生活——被困在一个荒岛上，只有自己相伴。搜寻或狩猎食物，从一个岛屿到另一个岛屿，并在夜幕降临时小心地建造木筏和庇护所——这些岛屿的夜晚可能会非常寒冷……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/1ce38082f5396878580d266c66e68df6.webp?t=1771887294\" width=508 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/80cc174edd83edc515c272ea72ab0fe6.poster.avif?t=1771887294\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/80cc174edd83edc515c272ea72ab0fe6.webm?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/80cc174edd83edc515c272ea72ab0fe6.mp4?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>至少，流落荒岛也有一些好处。探索美丽的太平洋风光。在闪耀的蓝色海水中游泳，站在金色的沙滩上，海浪拍打着你的双脚。当天气转变时，在棕榈树下避雨，听着雷声在头顶轰鸣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/045084e2420d6b43da9f5a0fbc01bb93.webp?t=1771887294\" width=294 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/22d3c61efebf4cb6446061970c024d00.poster.avif?t=1771887294\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/22d3c61efebf4cb6446061970c024d00.webm?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/22d3c61efebf4cb6446061970c024d00.mp4?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>利用周围的自然材料建造一个基地——这是你生存的关键。狩猎动物、砍伐树木、搜寻破损的船只，逐步建立安全的生存环境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/6eaba2087e927f6499d24ed38a7f19d1.webp?t=1771887294\" width=263 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/1cbf14ecb6309a8182c056342a08ffed.poster.avif?t=1771887294\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/1cbf14ecb6309a8182c056342a08ffed.webm?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/1cbf14ecb6309a8182c056342a08ffed.mp4?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你最好保持冷静——这些岛屿上很容易让人感到孤独，而流浪者往往会失去理智……保持精神稳定，确保充足的睡眠，否则可能会出现超自然现象，试图夺走你的生命。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/0075e2ef11473e18b7c8b3630b52003a.poster.avif?t=1771887294\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/0075e2ef11473e18b7c8b3630b52003a.webm?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713350/extras/0075e2ef11473e18b7c8b3630b52003a.mp4?t=1771887294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
